{"id": "figure_008", "modality": "figures", "name": "CLIP Dual-Encoder Contrastive Matrix", "task": {"description": "Create a single 1920x1080 self-contained HTML file using ONLY inline CSS and inline SVG that reproduces the CLIP contrastive pre-training figure. Title 'CLIP: Contrastive Language-Image Pre-training' at top in 32px bold. TOP-LEFT: a 'Text Encoder' (Transformer) box taking a column of N text inputs and producing N text embeddings T1..TN drawn as a horizontal row of small vectors across the TOP. LEFT side: an 'Image Encoder' (ResNet/ViT) box taking N images and producing N image embeddings I1..IN drawn as a vertical column of small vectors down the LEFT. In the center draw an N x N similarity matrix grid (use N = 4 or 5) where cell (i,j) = Ii \u00b7 Tj; the DIAGONAL cells (matched pairs) are highlighted/shaded differently from off-diagonal cells. Label the contrastive objective 'maximize diagonal, minimize off-diagonal (symmetric cross-entropy)'. The text-embedding row must align column-wise with the matrix columns, and the image-embedding column must align row-wise with the matrix rows. HARDEN (density + alignment): ALSO include (a) a LEGEND box that maps every distinct block color and every arrow/line style used in the figure, and (b) a small tensor-shape annotation on each major block (e.g. 'BxNxd'). Pack the figure densely with at least 14 labeled elements; every group of sibling blocks must be equal-size and share edges, with uniform gutters, and nothing may overlap or clip.", "requirements": ["Both encoders (Text Encoder, Image Encoder), the text-embedding row, the image-embedding column, and the N x N similarity matrix are all visible with no clipping at any edge", "No two boxes or matrix cells overlap each other", "Every label (T1..TN, I1..IN, encoder names) is fully contained inside its shape with no overflow", "The similarity matrix is a square grid with the SAME N for rows and columns (N consistent, 4 or 5), with no missing or extra cells", "The diagonal cells (matched pairs Ii\u00b7Ti) are visually highlighted/shaded differently from off-diagonal cells", "The text-embedding vectors T1..TN align column-wise with the matrix columns", "The image-embedding vectors I1..IN align row-wise with the matrix rows", "The contrastive-objective annotation is present, legible, and does not overlap the matrix or embeddings", "Matrix cells are evenly sized and evenly spaced (uniform grid)", "No element is within 10px of any viewport edge", "No horizontal or vertical scrollbar appears; all content fits inside 1920x1080", "A legend box maps every block color and arrow/line style used; each major block carries a tensor-shape annotation; sibling blocks are equal-size and edge-aligned with uniform gutters; no element overlaps or is clipped"]}, "runs": [{"run": 1, "ss_n_defects": 0, "ss_text_overlap": 0, "ss_clipped": 0, "ss_overflow": 0, "ss_total_tokens": 7088, "rv_n_defects": 1, "rv_text_overlap": 1, "rv_clipped": 0, "rv_overflow": 0, "rv_iterations": 3, "rv_total_tokens": 42609}, {"run": 2, "ss_n_defects": 0, "ss_text_overlap": 0, "ss_clipped": 0, "ss_overflow": 0, "ss_total_tokens": 6583, "rv_n_defects": 0, "rv_text_overlap": 0, "rv_clipped": 0, "rv_overflow": 0, "rv_iterations": 1, "rv_total_tokens": 6107}, {"run": 3, "ss_n_defects": 0, "ss_text_overlap": 0, "ss_clipped": 0, "ss_overflow": 0, "ss_total_tokens": 8763, "rv_n_defects": 0, "rv_text_overlap": 0, "rv_clipped": 0, "rv_overflow": 0, "rv_iterations": 1, "rv_total_tokens": 6996}], "ss_img": "images/figures/figure_008_ss.jpg", "rv_img": "images/figures/figure_008_rv.jpg", "ss_html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>CLIP: Contrastive Language-Image Pre-training</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 20px;\n            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n            background-color: #f8f9fa;\n            width: 1880px;\n            height: 1040px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        .title {\n            font-size: 32px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            text-align: center;\n            color: #2c3e50;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n        .tensor-shape {\n            font-size: 11px;\n            fill: #666;\n            font-style: italic;\n        }\n        .label-text {\n            font-size: 14px;\n            fill: #2c3e50;\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n        .small-label {\n            font-size: 12px;\n            fill: #34495e;\n        }\n        .objective-text {\n            font-size: 16px;\n            fill: #e74c3c;\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n        .legend-title {\n            font-size: 14px;\n            fill: #2c3e50;\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n        .legend-item {\n            font-size: 12px;\n            fill: #34495e;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"title\">CLIP: Contrastive Language-Image Pre-training</div>\n    \n    <svg width=\"1880\" height=\"980\" viewBox=\"0 0 1880 980\">\n        <!-- Text Inputs -->\n        <g id=\"text-inputs\">\n            <rect x=\"200\" y=\"80\" width=\"120\" height=\"30\" fill=\"#e8f4fd\" stroke=\"#3498db\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n            <text x=\"260\" y=\"100\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\">\"A dog playing\"</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"340\" y=\"80\" width=\"120\" height=\"30\" fill=\"#e8f4fd\" stroke=\"#3498db\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n            <text x=\"400\" y=\"100\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\">\"Cat on sofa\"</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"480\" y=\"80\" width=\"120\" height=\"30\" fill=\"#e8f4fd\" stroke=\"#3498db\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n            <text x=\"540\" y=\"100\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\">\"Bird flying\"</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"620\" y=\"80\" width=\"120\" height=\"30\" fill=\"#e8f4fd\" stroke=\"#3498db\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n            <text x=\"680\" y=\"100\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\">\"Fish swimming\"</text>\n        </g>\n        \n        <!-- Text Encoder -->\n        <g id=\"text-encoder\">\n            <rect x=\"200\" y=\"140\" width=\"540\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#3498db\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"3\" rx=\"8\"/>\n            <text x=\"470\" y=\"170\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"label-text\" fill=\"white\">Text Encoder (Transformer)</text>\n            <text x=\"470\" y=\"190\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"tensor-shape\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\">Input: Bx77 \u2192 Output: Bxd_text</text>\n            <text x=\"470\" y=\"205\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"tensor-shape\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\">4x512</text>\n        </g>\n        \n        <!-- Text Embeddings -->\n        <g id=\"text-embeddings\">\n            <rect x=\"200\" y=\"250\" width=\"120\" height=\"40\" fill=\"#2ecc71\" stroke=\"#27ae60\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n            <text x=\"260\" y=\"270\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\" fill=\"white\">T\u2081</text>\n            <text x=\"260\" y=\"285\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"tensor-shape\" fill=\"#a9dfbf\">512d</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"340\" y=\"250\" width=\"120\" height=\"40\" fill=\"#2ecc71\" stroke=\"#27ae60\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n            <text x=\"400\" y=\"270\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\" fill=\"white\">T\u2082</text>\n            <text x=\"400\" y=\"285\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"tensor-shape\" fill=\"#a9dfbf\">512d</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"480\" y=\"250\" width=\"120\" height=\"40\" fill=\"#2ecc71\" stroke=\"#27ae60\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n            <text x=\"540\" y=\"270\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\" fill=\"white\">T\u2083</text>\n            <text x=\"540\" y=\"285\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"tensor-shape\" fill=\"#a9dfbf\">512d</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"620\" y=\"250\" width=\"120\" height=\"40\" fill=\"#2ecc71\" stroke=\"#27ae60\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n            <text x=\"680\" y=\"270\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\" fill=\"white\">T\u2084</text>\n            <text x=\"680\" y=\"285\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"tensor-shape\" fill=\"#a9dfbf\">512d</text>\n        </g>\n        \n        <!-- Images -->\n        <g id=\"images\">\n            <rect x=\"80\" y=\"350\" width=\"80\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#fdeaa7\" stroke=\"#f39c12\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n            <text x=\"120\" y=\"395\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\">\ud83d\udc15</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"80\" y=\"450\" width=\"80\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#fdeaa7\" stroke=\"#f39c12\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n            <text x=\"120\" y=\"495\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\">\ud83d\udc31</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"80\" y=\"550\" width=\"80\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#fdeaa7\" stroke=\"#f39c12\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n            <text x=\"120\" y=\"595\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\">\ud83d\udc26</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"80\" y=\"650\" width=\"80\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#fdeaa7\" stroke=\"#f39c12\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n            <text x=\"120\" y=\"695\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\">\ud83d\udc20</text>\n        </g>\n        \n        <!-- Image Encoder -->\n        <g id=\"image-encoder\">\n            <rect x=\"80\" y=\"760\" width=\"80\" height=\"120\" fill=\"#e74c3c\" stroke=\"#c0392b\" stroke-width=\"3\" rx=\"8\"/>\n            <text x=\"120\" y=\"790\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"label-text\" fill=\"white\">Image</text>\n            <text x=\"120\" y=\"810\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"label-text\" fill=\"white\">Encoder</text>\n            <text x=\"120\" y=\"830\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"label-text\" fill=\"white\">(ResNet/</text>\n            <text x=\"120\" y=\"850\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"label-text\" fill=\"white\">ViT)</text>\n            <text x=\"120\" y=\"870\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"tensor-shape\" fill=\"#fadbd8\">Bx224x224x3</text>\n            <text x=\"120\" y=\"885\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"tensor-shape\" fill=\"#fadbd8\">\u2192 Bxd_img</text>\n        </g>\n        \n        <!-- Image Embeddings -->\n        <g id=\"image-embeddings\">\n            <rect x=\"200\" y=\"350\" width=\"40\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#9b59b6\" stroke=\"#8e44ad\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n            <text x=\"220\" y=\"385\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\" fill=\"white\">I\u2081</text>\n            <text x=\"220\" y=\"400\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"tensor-shape\" fill=\"#d7bde2\">512d</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"200\" y=\"450\" width=\"40\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#9b59b6\" stroke=\"#8e44ad\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n            <text x=\"220\" y=\"485\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\" fill=\"white\">I\u2082</text>\n            <text x=\"220\" y=\"500\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"tensor-shape\" fill=\"#d7bde2\">512d</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"200\" y=\"550\" width=\"40\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#9b59b6\" stroke=\"#8e44ad\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n            <text x=\"220\" y=\"585\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\" fill=\"white\">I\u2083</text>\n            <text x=\"220\" y=\"600\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"tensor-shape\" fill=\"#d7bde2\">512d</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"200\" y=\"650\" width=\"40\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#9b59b6\" stroke=\"#8e44ad\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n            <text x=\"220\" y=\"685\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\" fill=\"white\">I\u2084</text>\n            <text x=\"220\" y=\"700\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"tensor-shape\" fill=\"#d7bde2\">512d</text>\n        </g>\n        \n        <!-- Similarity Matrix -->\n        <g id=\"similarity-matrix\">\n            <!-- Matrix cells -->\n            <!-- Row 1 -->\n            <rect x=\"320\" y=\"350\" width=\"100\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#ff6b6b\" stroke=\"#e55656\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"370\" y=\"395\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\" fill=\"white\">I\u2081\u00b7T\u2081</text>\n            <rect x=\"440\" y=\"350\" width=\"100\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#74b9ff\" stroke=\"#0984e3\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"490\" y=\"395\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\" fill=\"white\">I\u2081\u00b7T\u2082</text>\n            <rect x=\"560\" y=\"350\" width=\"100\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#74b9ff\" stroke=\"#0984e3\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"610\" y=\"395\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\" fill=\"white\">I\u2081\u00b7T\u2083</text>\n            <rect x=\"680\" y=\"350\" width=\"100\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#74b9ff\" stroke=\"#0984e3\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"730\" y=\"395\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\" fill=\"white\">I\u2081\u00b7T\u2084</text>\n            \n            <!-- Row 2 -->\n            <rect x=\"320\" y=\"450\" width=\"100\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#74b9ff\" stroke=\"#0984e3\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"370\" y=\"495\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\" fill=\"white\">I\u2082\u00b7T\u2081</text>\n            <rect x=\"440\" y=\"450\" width=\"100\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#ff6b6b\" stroke=\"#e55656\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"490\" y=\"495\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\" fill=\"white\">I\u2082\u00b7T\u2082</text>\n            <rect x=\"560\" y=\"450\" width=\"100\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#74b9ff\" stroke=\"#0984e3\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"610\" y=\"495\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\" fill=\"white\">I\u2082\u00b7T\u2083</text>\n            <rect x=\"680\" y=\"450\" width=\"100\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#74b9ff\" stroke=\"#0984e3\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"730\" y=\"495\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\" fill=\"white\">I\u2082\u00b7T\u2084</text>\n            \n            <!-- Row 3 -->\n            <rect x=\"320\" y=\"550\" width=\"100\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#74b9ff\" stroke=\"#0984e3\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"370\" y=\"595\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\" fill=\"white\">I\u2083\u00b7T\u2081</text>\n            <rect x=\"440\" y=\"550\" width=\"100\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#74b9ff\" stroke=\"#0984e3\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"490\" y=\"595\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\" fill=\"white\">I\u2083\u00b7T\u2082</text>\n            <rect x=\"560\" y=\"550\" width=\"100\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#ff6b6b\" stroke=\"#e55656\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"610\" y=\"595\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\" fill=\"white\">I\u2083\u00b7T\u2083</text>\n            <rect x=\"680\" y=\"550\" width=\"100\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#74b9ff\" stroke=\"#0984e3\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"730\" y=\"595\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\" fill=\"white\">I\u2083\u00b7T\u2084</text>\n            \n            <!-- Row 4 -->\n            <rect x=\"320\" y=\"650\" width=\"100\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#74b9ff\" stroke=\"#0984e3\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"370\" y=\"695\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\" fill=\"white\">I\u2084\u00b7T\u2081</text>\n            <rect x=\"440\" y=\"650\" width=\"100\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#74b9ff\" stroke=\"#0984e3\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"490\" y=\"695\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\" fill=\"white\">I\u2084\u00b7T\u2082</text>\n            <rect x=\"560\" y=\"650\" width=\"100\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#74b9ff\" stroke=\"#0984e3\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"610\" y=\"695\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\" fill=\"white\">I\u2084\u00b7T\u2083</text>\n            <rect x=\"680\" y=\"650\" width=\"100\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#ff6b6b\" stroke=\"#e55656\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"730\" y=\"695\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\" fill=\"white\">I\u2084\u00b7T\u2084</text>\n            \n            <!-- Matrix label -->\n            <text x=\"500\" y=\"340\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"label-text\">Similarity Matrix (4\u00d74)</text>\n            <text x=\"500\" y=\"320\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"tensor-shape\">cosine_similarity(I, T)</text>\n        </g>\n        \n        <!-- Contrastive Objective -->\n        <g id=\"objective\">\n            <rect x=\"850\" y=\"450\" width=\"300\" height=\"120\" fill=\"#fff3cd\" stroke=\"#ffc107\" stroke-width=\"3\" rx=\"8\"/>\n            <text x=\"1000\" y=\"480\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"label-text\">Contrastive Objective</text>\n            <text x=\"1000\" y=\"505\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"objective-text\">Maximize Diagonal</text>\n            <text x=\"1000\" y=\"525\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"objective-text\">Minimize Off-diagonal</text>\n            <text x=\"1000\" y=\"550\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\">(Symmetric Cross-entropy)</text>\n        </g>\n        \n        <!-- Arrows -->\n        <!-- Text inputs to encoder -->\n        <path d=\"M 260 110 L 260 140\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 400 110 L 400 140\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 540 110 L 540 140\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 680 110 L 680 140\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        \n        <!-- Text encoder to embeddings -->\n        <path d=\"M 260 220 L 260 250\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 400 220 L 400 250\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 540 220 L 540 250\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 680 220 L 680 250\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        \n        <!-- Images to encoder -->\n        <path d=\"M 120 430 L 120 760\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 120 530 L 120 760\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 120 630 L 120 760\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 120 730 L 120 760\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        \n        <!-- Image encoder to embeddings -->\n        <path d=\"M 160 390 L 200 390\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 160 490 L 200 490\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 160 590 L 200 590\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 160 690 L 200 690\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        \n        <!-- Embeddings to matrix -->\n        <path d=\"M 240 390 L 320 390\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 240 490 L 320 490\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 240 590 L 320 590\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 240 690 L 320 690\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        \n        <path d=\"M 260 290 L 370 350\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 400 290 L 490 350\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 540 290 L 610 350\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 680 290 L 730 350\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        \n        <!-- Legend -->\n        <g id=\"legend\">\n            <rect x=\"1200\" y=\"80\" width=\"300\" height=\"400\" fill=\"#ffffff\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n            <text x=\"1350\" y=\"110\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"legend-title\">Legend</text>\n            \n            <!-- Color legend -->\n            <rect x=\"1220\" y=\"130\" width=\"20\" height=\"15\" fill=\"#e8f4fd\" stroke=\"#3498db\"/>\n            <text x=\"1250\" y=\"142\" class=\"legend-item\">Text Input</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"1220\" y=\"155\" width=\"20\" height=\"15\" fill=\"#3498db\"/>\n            <text x=\"1250\" y=\"167\" class=\"legend-item\">Text Encoder</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"1220\" y=\"180\" width=\"20\" height=\"15\" fill=\"#2ecc71\"/>\n            <text x=\"1250\" y=\"192\" class=\"legend-item\">Text Embedding</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"1220\" y=\"205\" width=\"20\" height=\"15\" fill=\"#fdeaa7\" stroke=\"#f39c12\"/>\n            <text x=\"1250\" y=\"217\" class=\"legend-item\">Image Input</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"1220\" y=\"230\" width=\"20\" height=\"15\" fill=\"#e74c3c\"/>\n            <text x=\"1250\" y=\"242\" class=\"legend-item\">Image Encoder</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"1220\" y=\"255\" width=\"20\" height=\"15\" fill=\"#9b59b6\"/>\n            <text x=\"1250\" y=\"267\" class=\"legend-item\">Image Embedding</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"1220\" y=\"280\" width=\"20\" height=\"15\" fill=\"#ff6b6b\"/>\n            <text x=\"1250\" y=\"292\" class=\"legend-item\">Matched Pairs (High)</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"1220\" y=\"305\" width=\"20\" height=\"15\" fill=\"#74b9ff\"/>\n            <text x=\"1250\" y=\"317\" class=\"legend-item\">Unmatched (Low)</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"1220\" y=\"330\" width=\"20\" height=\"15\" fill=\"#fff3cd\" stroke=\"#ffc107\"/>\n            <text x=\"1250\" y=\"342\" class=\"legend-item\">Objective Function</text>\n            \n            <!-- Arrow legend -->\n            <line x1=\"1220\" y1=\"365\" x2=\"1240\" y2=\"365\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            <text x=\"1250\" y=\"370\" class=\"legend-item\">Data Flow</text>\n            \n            <!-- Tensor shapes -->\n            <text x=\"1220\" y=\"395\" class=\"legend-item\">Tensor Shapes:</text>\n            <text x=\"1220\" y=\"410\" class=\"legend-item\">B = Batch size (4)</text>\n            <text x=\"1220\" y=\"425\" class=\"legend-item\">d = Embedding dim (512)</text>\n            <text x=\"1220\" y=\"440\" class=\"legend-item\">77 = Max text tokens</text>\n            <text x=\"1220\" y=\"455\" class=\"legend-item\">224\u00d7224\u00d73 = Image size</text>\n        </g>\n        \n        <!-- Arrow marker definition -->\n        <defs>\n            <marker id=\"arrowhead\" markerWidth=\"10\" markerHeight=\"7\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\">\n                <polygon points=\"0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7\" fill=\"#2c3e50\"/>\n            </marker>\n        </defs>\n    </svg>\n</body>\n</html>", "rv_html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>CLIP: Contrastive Language-Image Pre-training</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 20px;\n            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n            background-color: #f8f9fa;\n            width: 1880px;\n            height: 1040px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        .title {\n            font-size: 32px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            text-align: center;\n            color: #2c3e50;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n        .tensor-shape {\n            font-size: 11px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            fill: #34495e;\n        }\n        .label-text {\n            font-size: 14px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            fill: #2c3e50;\n        }\n        .small-label {\n            font-size: 12px;\n            fill: #34495e;\n        }\n        .objective-text {\n            font-size: 16px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            fill: #e74c3c;\n        }\n        .legend-text {\n            font-size: 12px;\n            fill: #2c3e50;\n        }\n        .legend-title {\n            font-size: 14px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            fill: #2c3e50;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"title\">CLIP: Contrastive Language-Image Pre-training</div>\n    \n    <svg width=\"1880\" height=\"980\" viewBox=\"0 0 1880 980\">\n        <!-- Text Inputs -->\n        <g id=\"text-inputs\">\n            <rect x=\"200\" y=\"80\" width=\"120\" height=\"40\" fill=\"#3498db\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n            <text x=\"260\" y=\"105\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\" fill=\"white\">\"A dog playing\"</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"340\" y=\"80\" width=\"120\" height=\"40\" fill=\"#3498db\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n            <text x=\"400\" y=\"105\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\" fill=\"white\">\"Cat on sofa\"</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"480\" y=\"80\" width=\"120\" height=\"40\" fill=\"#3498db\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n            <text x=\"540\" y=\"105\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\" fill=\"white\">\"Bird flying\"</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"620\" y=\"80\" width=\"120\" height=\"40\" fill=\"#3498db\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n            <text x=\"680\" y=\"105\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\" fill=\"white\">\"Car driving\"</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"760\" y=\"80\" width=\"120\" height=\"40\" fill=\"#3498db\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n            <text x=\"820\" y=\"105\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\" fill=\"white\">\"Tree in park\"</text>\n        </g>\n        \n        <!-- Text Encoder -->\n        <rect x=\"200\" y=\"150\" width=\"680\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#9b59b6\" stroke=\"#8e44ad\" stroke-width=\"3\" rx=\"8\"/>\n        <text x=\"540\" y=\"180\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"label-text\" fill=\"white\">Text Encoder (Transformer)</text>\n        <text x=\"540\" y=\"200\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"tensor-shape\" fill=\"white\">Input: Bx77 \u2192 Output: BxNxd</text>\n        <text x=\"540\" y=\"215\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\" fill=\"white\">Multi-head Self-Attention + Feed Forward</text>\n        \n        <!-- Arrows from text inputs to encoder -->\n        <path d=\"M 260 120 L 260 150\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 400 120 L 400 150\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 540 120 L 540 150\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 680 120 L 680 150\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 820 120 L 820 150\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        \n        <!-- Text Embeddings -->\n        <g id=\"text-embeddings\">\n            <rect x=\"240\" y=\"260\" width=\"40\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#e67e22\" stroke=\"#d35400\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n            <text x=\"260\" y=\"285\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\" fill=\"white\">T\u2081</text>\n            <text x=\"260\" y=\"300\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"tensor-shape\" fill=\"white\">512d</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"380\" y=\"260\" width=\"40\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#e67e22\" stroke=\"#d35400\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n            <text x=\"400\" y=\"285\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\" fill=\"white\">T\u2082</text>\n            <text x=\"400\" y=\"300\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"tensor-shape\" fill=\"white\">512d</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"520\" y=\"260\" width=\"40\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#e67e22\" stroke=\"#d35400\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n            <text x=\"540\" y=\"285\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\" fill=\"white\">T\u2083</text>\n            <text x=\"540\" y=\"300\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"tensor-shape\" fill=\"white\">512d</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"660\" y=\"260\" width=\"40\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#e67e22\" stroke=\"#d35400\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n            <text x=\"680\" y=\"285\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\" fill=\"white\">T\u2084</text>\n            <text x=\"680\" y=\"300\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"tensor-shape\" fill=\"white\">512d</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"800\" y=\"260\" width=\"40\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#e67e22\" stroke=\"#d35400\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n            <text x=\"820\" y=\"285\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\" fill=\"white\">T\u2085</text>\n            <text x=\"820\" y=\"300\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"tensor-shape\" fill=\"white\">512d</text>\n        </g>\n        \n        <!-- Arrows from text encoder to embeddings -->\n        <path d=\"M 260 230 L 260 260\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 400 230 L 400 260\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 540 230 L 540 260\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 680 230 L 680 260\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 820 230 L 820 260\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        \n        <!-- Images -->\n        <g id=\"images\">\n            <rect x=\"40\" y=\"200\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#27ae60\" stroke=\"#229954\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n            <text x=\"70\" y=\"235\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\" fill=\"white\">\ud83d\udc15</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"40\" y=\"280\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#27ae60\" stroke=\"#229954\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n            <text x=\"70\" y=\"315\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\" fill=\"white\">\ud83d\udc31</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"40\" y=\"360\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#27ae60\" stroke=\"#229954\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n            <text x=\"70\" y=\"395\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\" fill=\"white\">\ud83d\udc26</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"40\" y=\"440\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#27ae60\" stroke=\"#229954\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n            <text x=\"70\" y=\"475\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\" fill=\"white\">\ud83d\ude97</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"40\" y=\"520\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#27ae60\" stroke=\"#229954\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n            <text x=\"70\" y=\"555\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\" fill=\"white\">\ud83c\udf33</text>\n        </g>\n        \n        <!-- Image Encoder -->\n        <rect x=\"120\" y=\"200\" width=\"80\" height=\"380\" fill=\"#1abc9c\" stroke=\"#16a085\" stroke-width=\"3\" rx=\"8\"/>\n        <text x=\"160\" y=\"230\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"label-text\" fill=\"white\">Image</text>\n        <text x=\"160\" y=\"250\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"label-text\" fill=\"white\">Encoder</text>\n        <text x=\"160\" y=\"270\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\" fill=\"white\">(ResNet/ViT)</text>\n        <text x=\"160\" y=\"290\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"tensor-shape\" fill=\"white\">Input:</text>\n        <text x=\"160\" y=\"305\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"tensor-shape\" fill=\"white\">Bx224x224x3</text>\n        <text x=\"160\" y=\"330\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"tensor-shape\" fill=\"white\">\u2193</text>\n        <text x=\"160\" y=\"350\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"tensor-shape\" fill=\"white\">Output:</text>\n        <text x=\"160\" y=\"365\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"tensor-shape\" fill=\"white\">BxNxd</text>\n        <text x=\"160\" y=\"390\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\" fill=\"white\">Conv Layers</text>\n        <text x=\"160\" y=\"405\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\" fill=\"white\">+</text>\n        <text x=\"160\" y=\"420\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\" fill=\"white\">Global Pool</text>\n        <text x=\"160\" y=\"435\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\" fill=\"white\">+</text>\n        <text x=\"160\" y=\"450\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\" fill=\"white\">Linear Proj</text>\n        \n        <!-- Arrows from images to encoder -->\n        <path d=\"M 100 230 L 120 230\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 100 310 L 120 310\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 100 390 L 120 390\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 100 470 L 120 470\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 100 550 L 120 550\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        \n        <!-- Image Embeddings -->\n        <g id=\"image-embeddings\">\n            <rect x=\"220\" y=\"210\" width=\"60\" height=\"40\" fill=\"#f39c12\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n            <text x=\"250\" y=\"225\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\" fill=\"white\">I\u2081</text>\n            <text x=\"250\" y=\"240\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"tensor-shape\" fill=\"white\">512d</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"220\" y=\"290\" width=\"60\" height=\"40\" fill=\"#f39c12\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n            <text x=\"250\" y=\"305\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\" fill=\"white\">I\u2082</text>\n            <text x=\"250\" y=\"320\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"tensor-shape\" fill=\"white\">512d</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"220\" y=\"370\" width=\"60\" height=\"40\" fill=\"#f39c12\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n            <text x=\"250\" y=\"385\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\" fill=\"white\">I\u2083</text>\n            <text x=\"250\" y=\"400\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"tensor-shape\" fill=\"white\">512d</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"220\" y=\"450\" width=\"60\" height=\"40\" fill=\"#f39c12\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n            <text x=\"250\" y=\"465\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\" fill=\"white\">I\u2084</text>\n            <text x=\"250\" y=\"480\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"tensor-shape\" fill=\"white\">512d</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"220\" y=\"530\" width=\"60\" height=\"40\" fill=\"#f39c12\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n            <text x=\"250\" y=\"545\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\" fill=\"white\">I\u2085</text>\n            <text x=\"250\" y=\"560\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"tensor-shape\" fill=\"white\">512d</text>\n        </g>\n        \n        <!-- Arrows from image encoder to embeddings -->\n        <path d=\"M 200 230 L 220 230\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 200 310 L 220 310\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 200 390 L 220 390\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 200 470 L 220 470\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 200 550 L 220 550\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        \n        <!-- Similarity Matrix (5x5) -->\n        <g id=\"similarity-matrix\">\n            <!-- Matrix cells -->\n            <!-- Row 1 -->\n            <rect x=\"300\" y=\"350\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" fill=\"#e74c3c\" stroke=\"#c0392b\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"325\" y=\"380\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\" fill=\"white\">0.9</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"360\" y=\"350\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"385\" y=\"380\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\">0.1</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"420\" y=\"350\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"445\" y=\"380\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\">0.2</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"480\" y=\"350\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"505\" y=\"380\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\">0.1</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"540\" y=\"350\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"565\" y=\"380\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\">0.0</text>\n            \n            <!-- Row 2 -->\n            <rect x=\"300\" y=\"410\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"325\" y=\"440\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\">0.2</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"360\" y=\"410\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" fill=\"#e74c3c\" stroke=\"#c0392b\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"385\" y=\"440\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\" fill=\"white\">0.8</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"420\" y=\"410\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"445\" y=\"440\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\">0.1</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"480\" y=\"410\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"505\" y=\"440\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\">0.0</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"540\" y=\"410\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"565\" y=\"440\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\">0.1</text>\n            \n            <!-- Row 3 -->\n            <rect x=\"300\" y=\"470\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"325\" y=\"500\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\">0.1</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"360\" y=\"470\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"385\" y=\"500\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\">0.0</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"420\" y=\"470\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" fill=\"#e74c3c\" stroke=\"#c0392b\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"445\" y=\"500\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\" fill=\"white\">0.9</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"480\" y=\"470\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"505\" y=\"500\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\">0.2</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"540\" y=\"470\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"565\" y=\"500\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\">0.1</text>\n            \n            <!-- Row 4 -->\n            <rect x=\"300\" y=\"530\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"325\" y=\"560\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\">0.0</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"360\" y=\"530\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"385\" y=\"560\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\">0.1</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"420\" y=\"530\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"445\" y=\"560\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\">0.1</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"480\" y=\"530\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" fill=\"#e74c3c\" stroke=\"#c0392b\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"505\" y=\"560\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\" fill=\"white\">0.8</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"540\" y=\"530\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"565\" y=\"560\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\">0.2</text>\n            \n            <!-- Row 5 -->\n            <rect x=\"300\" y=\"590\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"325\" y=\"620\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\">0.1</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"360\" y=\"590\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"385\" y=\"620\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\">0.0</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"420\" y=\"590\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"445\" y=\"620\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\">0.1</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"480\" y=\"590\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"505\" y=\"620\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\">0.2</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"540\" y=\"590\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" fill=\"#e74c3c\" stroke=\"#c0392b\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"565\" y=\"620\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"small-label\" fill=\"white\">0.9</text>\n        </g>\n        \n        <!-- Matrix Labels -->\n        <text x=\"425\" y=\"340\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"label-text\">Similarity Matrix (I\u00b7T)</text>\n        <text x=\"425\" y=\"660\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"tensor-shape\">5\u00d75 Cosine Similarities</text>\n        \n        <!-- Contrastive Objective -->\n        <text x=\"425\" y=\"700\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"objective-text\">Maximize diagonal, minimize off-diagonal</text>\n        <text x=\"425\" y=\"720\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"objective-text\">(Symmetric Cross-Entropy Loss)</text>\n        \n        <!-- Connecting lines from embeddings to matrix -->\n        <!-- From text embeddings to matrix columns -->\n        <path d=\"M 260 320 L 325 350\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke-dasharray=\"5,5\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 400 320 L 385 350\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke-dasharray=\"5,5\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 540 320 L 445 350\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke-dasharray=\"5,5\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 680 320 L 505 350\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke-dasharray=\"5,5\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 820 320 L 565 350\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke-dasharray=\"5,5\"/>\n        \n        <!-- From image embeddings to matrix rows -->\n        <path d=\"M 280 230 L 300 375\" stroke=\"#f39c12\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke-dasharray=\"5,5\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 280 310 L 300 435\" stroke=\"#f39c12\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke-dasharray=\"5,5\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 280 390 L 300 495\" stroke=\"#f39c12\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke-dasharray=\"5,5\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 280 470 L 300 555\" stroke=\"#f39c12\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke-dasharray=\"5,5\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 280 550 L 300 615\" stroke=\"#f39c12\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke-dasharray=\"5,5\"/>\n        \n        <!-- Legend -->\n        <g id=\"legend\">\n            <rect x=\"1400\" y=\"100\" width=\"450\" height=\"600\" fill=\"#ffffff\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n            <text x=\"1625\" y=\"130\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"legend-title\">LEGEND</text>\n            \n            <!-- Color Legend -->\n            <text x=\"1420\" y=\"160\" class=\"legend-text\">Colors:</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"1420\" y=\"170\" width=\"20\" height=\"15\" fill=\"#3498db\"/>\n            <text x=\"1450\" y=\"182\" class=\"legend-text\">Text Input</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"1420\" y=\"195\" width=\"20\" height=\"15\" fill=\"#9b59b6\"/>\n            <text x=\"1450\" y=\"207\" class=\"legend-text\">Text Encoder (Transformer)</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"1420\" y=\"220\" width=\"20\" height=\"15\" fill=\"#e67e22\"/>\n            <text x=\"1450\" y=\"232\" class=\"legend-text\">Text Embeddings</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"1420\" y=\"245\" width=\"20\" height=\"15\" fill=\"#27ae60\"/>\n            <text x=\"1450\" y=\"257\" class=\"legend-text\">Image Input</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"1420\" y=\"270\" width=\"20\" height=\"15\" fill=\"#1abc9c\"/>\n            <text x=\"1450\" y=\"282\" class=\"legend-text\">Image Encoder (ResNet/ViT)</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"1420\" y=\"295\" width=\"20\" height=\"15\" fill=\"#f39c12\"/>\n            <text x=\"1450\" y=\"307\" class=\"legend-text\">Image Embeddings</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"1420\" y=\"320\" width=\"20\" height=\"15\" fill=\"#e74c3c\"/>\n            <text x=\"1450\" y=\"332\" class=\"legend-text\">High Similarity (Diagonal)</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"1420\" y=\"345\" width=\"20\" height=\"15\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\"/>\n            <text x=\"1450\" y=\"357\" class=\"legend-text\">Low Similarity (Off-diagonal)</text>\n            \n            <!-- Line Styles -->\n            <text x=\"1420\" y=\"390\" class=\"legend-text\">Line Styles:</text>\n            \n            <line x1=\"1420\" y1=\"405\" x2=\"1460\" y2=\"405\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            <text x=\"1470\" y=\"410\" class=\"legend-text\">Data Flow</text>\n            \n            <line x1=\"1420\" y1=\"425\" x2=\"1460\" y2=\"425\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-dasharray=\"5,5\"/>\n            <text x=\"1470\" y=\"430\" class=\"legend-text\">Text Embedding Connection</text>\n            \n            <line x1=\"1420\" y1=\"445\" x2=\"1460\" y2=\"445\" stroke=\"#f39c12\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-dasharray=\"5,5\"/>\n            <text x=\"1470\" y=\"450\" class=\"legend-text\">Image Embedding Connection</text>\n            \n            <!-- Tensor Shapes -->\n            <text x=\"1420\" y=\"480\" class=\"legend-text\">Tensor Shapes:</text>\n            <text x=\"1420\" y=\"500\" class=\"legend-text\">B = Batch size</text>\n            <text x=\"1420\" y=\"520\" class=\"legend-text\">N = Number of samples</text>\n            <text x=\"1420\" y=\"540\" class=\"legend-text\">d = Embedding dimension (512)</text>\n            <text x=\"1420\" y=\"560\" class=\"legend-text\">77 = Max text sequence length</text>\n            <text x=\"1420\" y=\"580\" class=\"legend-text\">224\u00d7224\u00d73 = Image dimensions</text>\n            \n            <!-- Process Flow -->\n            <text x=\"1420\" y=\"610\" class=\"legend-text\">Process:</text>\n            <text x=\"1420\" y=\"630\" class=\"legend-text\">1. Encode text and images</text>\n            <text x=\"1420\" y=\"650\" class=\"legend-text\">2. Compute similarity matrix</text>\n            <text x=\"1420\" y=\"670\" class=\"legend-text\">3. Apply contrastive loss</text>\n        </g>\n        \n        <!-- Arrow marker definition -->\n        <defs>\n            <marker id=\"arrowhead\" markerWidth=\"10\" markerHeight=\"7\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\">\n                <polygon points=\"0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7\" fill=\"#2c3e50\"/>\n            </marker>\n        </defs>\n    </svg>\n</body>\n</html>"}